270
00:41:33,640 --> 00:41:35,699
I wish he was here now.

271
00:41:42,950 --> 00:41:47,046
Wherever he may be,
you are in his thoughts.

272
00:42:01,435 --> 00:42:03,801
Part of him will always be here.

273
