In our profession,
we shouldn't trust anyone.

277
00:43:19,913 --> 00:43:21,642
How did they know
about that beach?

278
00:43:21,715 --> 00:43:24,411
They might have followed me...

279
00:43:24,484 --> 00:43:26,145
when I drove there.

280
00:43:26,219 --> 00:43:28,016
That's my fault.

281
00:43:29,389 --> 00:43:30,515
Who wants me dead?

282
00:43:31,491 --> 00:43:33,425
Why do you ask?

283
00:43:35,028 --> 00:43:37,394
You know the rules.

284
00:43:39,700 --> 00:43:42,794
Why didn't you leave town
after the job?

285
00:43:42,869 --> 00:43:44,359
I haven't got my money yet.

286
00:45:53,200 --> 00:45:55,134
Who wants me dead?

287
00:45:55,202 --> 00:45:59,639
